bhai jaan ( 1945 film ) is a bollywood film .   it was released on 15 september 1945 in bombay . directed by syed khalil .   the actors were karan dewan , noor jehan , anees khatoon , meena shorey , shah nawaz , ansari and nazir .   it was a family drama , made under a banner of united films .   the print has been lost now . 1945 .   the film a muslim social family drama , is about two brothers ( shah nawaz and karan dewan ) in love with a dancing girl ( noor jehan ) , which disrupts their family life .   it leads to the girl consuming poison in order to maintain the respectability of the brothers ' family name .